<h2 id="hd_id3154984">Illumination</h2>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3155391" xml-lang="en-US">Specify the light source for the object, as well as the color of the light source and of the ambient light. You can define up to eight different light sources.</paragraph>
