<h2 id="hd_id3153748">Light source</h2>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149149" xml-lang="en-US"><ahelp hid="svx/ui/docking3deffects/light8">Click twice to turn the light source on, and then select a color for the light from the list. If you want, you can also set the color of the surrounding light, by selecting a color from the <emph>Ambient light</emph> box.</ahelp> You can also press the Spacebar to turn the light source on or off. </paragraph>
